c: 18
v: 109
t: Takheun le gata wahai Muhammad Ubak dum umat meunoe tapeugah Meunyo ie laot bandum meusapat Teuma geusurat kalimat Allah Habeh ie laot keudua meuhat ‘Eleumee Hadharat hana lom sudah Sangkira neubri daweuet lom le that Beu sadum meuhat ngon laot luah Han ek cit habeh ilmee Hadharat Dumnankeuh le that kalimat Allah